  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA100">
<l>ōraṭiyuñ cāṭutaitta voṇmalar cēvaṭiyu</l>
<l>mīraṭiyuṅ kāṇalā meṉṉeñcē – yōraṭiyiṟ</l>
<l>ṟāyavaṉaik kēcavaṉait taṇṭuḻāy mālaicēr</l>
<l>māyavaṉai yēmaṉattu vai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>One foot that kicked the cart  and a bright red flower foot,</l>
<l>two feet are there to see, my heart. Towards the one who extended</l> 
<l>one foot, Kēcavaṉ, the cunning one joined by a garland</l>
<l>of cool tulsi direct your mind.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
